high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the where the coffee machine is on the counter, then turn left.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the counter.
Put the head of lettuce in the fridge to get cold, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take out the chilled head of lettuce.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, turn right before the oven to face the counter.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the back of the counter to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sink then turn left and go towards the counter and then turn left
Pick up the lettuce from the counter
Turn left and make your way to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge to chill, then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn left to go just past the fridge then turn right
Put the lettuce at the back of the counter, next to the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled lettuce on the counter next to the stove

high_descs: Turn around and go forward and the turn to the left to face the counter to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick the lettuce up from the counter.
Turn left and cross the room to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the lettuce out and shut the door again.
Go left and then turn right to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.
